<div class=3D"hero">
  <p class=3D"hero-eyebrow">Principal Product Manager</p>
  <h1>Pooja Tyagi</h1>
  <p class=3D"hero-sub">10+ years building enterprise platform strategy at =
scale. From authentication and API governance to LLM-powered analytics =E2=
=80=94 owning complex product areas end-to-end and shipping outcomes that m=
ove businesses forward.</p>
